_sText:
My map, finally ported from CS:GO to CS:S.

It's completion duration is below 60 seconds and its difficulty has been called tier 2-3 by beta testers.

This map is just a test if people like gameplay with strafe objectives, I wasn't really focusing on design. I will most likely create surf_strafe2 in the future and focus more on design and map lenght after I collect feedback from players.

Have fun.
